## MCP Tools (optional but recommended)

- **code-review-graph**: semantic code search, impact radius, decision-ledger reconciliation
- **context7**: library/framework docs lookup (prevents hallucinated APIs)
- **agentdb (claude-flow)**: `agentdb_pattern_store` / `agentdb_pattern_search` — cross-run memory
